<item>
            <title>[LU-18155] Improve Lustre debugging macros</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18155</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Lustre debugging macros shouldn&apos;t duplicate pre-existing Linux debugging features. They should try to mirror the semantics of the Linux kernel. They should be consistently and correctly used across all of Lustre. Debugging infrastructure shouldn&apos;t require a recompilation, if possible.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
